<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.5.4">
<l>nīṅkanillāk kaṇṇa nīrkaḷeṉ ṟaṉṉaiyaru muṉitir.</l>
<l>tēṉkoḷ cōlait tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi nampiyai nāṉkaṇṭapiṉ</l>
<l>pūntaṇ mālait taṇṭuḻāyum poṉmuṭi yumvaṭivum</l>
<l>pāṅku tōṉṟum paṭṭu nāṇum pāviyēṉ pakkattavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“When they depart tears are in [your] eyes, unstopping”, so you all will disapprove, mothers.</l>
<l>After I saw Nampi of Tirukkuṟuṅkuṭi with honey-rich groves,</l>
<l>the garland cool with flowers, the cool Tulsi, the gold crown, [his] shape</l>
<l>the silk threads that appear at [his] side are close to me evildoer.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
